fail_def_hidden_dummy_all_elim_ctx_pool_exhausted
--------------------------------------------------

l1: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ alpha) , (x ~ x) ⊢
  mono f $ by ax
l2: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ alpha) , (x ~ x) ⊢
  ∀ y ((f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ f ∘ y) → (h ∘ alpha ~ y)) $ by all_elim [l1]
